claim.claim-text:
1. A container comprising; 
a main body which is arranged to store items; 
a door on the main body mounted for pivotal movement about a vertical axis at one side which allows the door to be opened and closed sideways; 
and a bracket on the door for use in opening the door; 
wherein the bracket is coupled to the door at a bottom corner of the door remote from the pivot axis and wherein the bracket provides an abutment element which is arranged to project from the door such that the element can be engaged by a person's foot.
